message.body: I think u might be ok with Sunday at the gym.
Yeah, I thought it might be dead-ish on Sundays. All working out what to do for midweek though and getting nowhere...

I'm no expert but I'm will to help in any way I can. I did some of the stuff ######## showed us and a few more machines. It is a learning process but I'm hoping to get into a regular routine. Join me whenever u want!
